{"tid":2489639,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣出道17年首度參演大河劇 扮小栗旬初戀情人","createTime":"2021-04-15T05:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T05:23:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08879393ee346aad3012d3a1ef73c8eb0705bce6","tid":2489639,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zHtqtMW-Bri0V8UKrH1P9AA9qas=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q4VHZGLZCJBU7JUKZXORMG5LA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzHtqtMW-Bri0V8UKrH1P9AA9qas%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ4VHZGLZCJBU7JUKZXORMG5LA4.jpg&h=3baab301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本「國民老婆」新垣結衣落實參演明年播放的NHK大河劇《鎌倉殿的13人》，是她出道做演員17年以來首次演出的大河劇，在劇中飾演男主角小栗旬的初戀情人。<br />\n<br />\n大河劇《鎌倉殿的13人》由三谷幸喜負責編劇，小栗旬擔任男主角，扮演鎌倉幕府的第二代執權北條義時。《鎌》劇的官方Twitter今日第二次公佈演員名單，新垣結衣、佐藤浩市和西田敏行將會參與演出，新垣結衣飾演北條義時的初戀情人八重，她後來卻成為由大泉洋飾演的鐮倉幕府首任將軍源賴朝的妻子。《鎌》劇陣容頂盛，除了小栗旬和新垣結衣外，影帝菅田將暉、中村獅童、宮澤理惠、小池榮子、山本耕史等亦有份演出。結衣BB表示，在眾多不同的說法中，雖然只有部份的片段，但當她認識八重的人生後，內心亦感到震撼，所以十分期待今次演出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MCFPK1pvZjXdgx6TCqimPZkEJJg=/802x923/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XJMCCZEE4NG5LILAFMDDMNXEPI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMCFPK1pvZjXdgx6TCqimPZkEJJg%3D%2F802x923%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXJMCCZEE4NG5LILAFMDDMNXEPI.JPG&h=994cca07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0pRU7kA1xB_qj6W9TMCKvI2zSq0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NOF4OEHYEFBMHIIC2Y2Z2GUJLQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.co